room_title: Escape room "Contagion" by The Escape Room Indianapolis in Indianapolis
review: We did the very hard Contagion! Cathleen was an awesome host! Thanks for a great time.

room_title: Escape room "Contagion" by The Escape Room Indianapolis in Indianapolis
review: We went tonight to the new Contagion room! We escaped with about 11 minutes left and our guide, Anthony, told us we were the fastest all week!! This whole idea is such a good concept. The mastermind behind these rooms is so creative! And our guide Anthony was so awesome!
